                      "text": "Cowboys VS Cyborgs",
                      "marks": [
                        "bold",
                        "display"
                      ],
                      "color": "#14191d"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " is a web-based game developed as part of an academic project, inspired by the movie ",
                      "color": "#14191d"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Cowboys & Aliens",
                      "color": "#14191d",
                      "href": "http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0409847/"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ", and designed to combine classic tower defense mechanics with thematic elements from the film.\n",
                      "color": "#14191d"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "kind": "paragraph",
                  "inlines": [
                    {
                      "text": "This project was developed by a multidisciplinary team of students from Art and Animation, Game Design, and Software Development, aiming to create an engaging gameplay experience that blends sci-fi and Western aesthetics.",
                      "color": "#14191d"
                    },
